      <title>小队成员布什在失败后誓言要与亲以色列组织作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/pro-israel-group-s-funding-helps-oust-a-second-squad-member</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议员科里·布什表示​​，由于民主党在加沙战争问题上的分歧，她在初选战中惨败，且代价高昂，她将对美国以色列公共事务委员会采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/pro-israel-group-s-funding-helps-oust-a-second-squad-member</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国准备应对更多因虚假信息引发的极右翼骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方准备在英国各地部署数千名警员，因为极右翼团体策划了数十场示威活动，这将成为对首相基尔·斯塔默平息最近一波反移民骚乱的努力的一次关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
